@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using Bookme.Data.Models
@inject SignInManager<ApplicationUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li>
            <div class="dropdown nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-dark dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" style="cursor: pointer">Settings</a>
                <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
                    @if (this.User.IsInRole(""))
                    {

                    }
                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="OfferedServices" asp-action="All">My Services</a>
                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="OfferedServices" asp-action="Add">Add new service</a>
                    <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">My Bookings</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" title="Manage">Account</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action("Index", "Home", new { area = "" })">
                <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register">Register</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login">Login</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>
